{
  "stem": "107.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was very much interested in how these people look back, now, at this time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But the only way, I guess, they can live with themselves is by denying it or saying it may not have been.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that was an intelligent man, a man who had a doctorate in political science.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "His wife, who was a much simpler woman, was much more sympathetic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Anyway, he is 80 years old, like I am.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were very touched to meet each other again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But that area is cut.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The university was in Prague, which is the-- was and is the capital of the country.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that univ-- even though it was in the middle of a Czech area, there were two universities.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One was a German university, where I was, and the other was the Czech university.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And curious enough, there were many Jewish professors in the German university.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were very few Jewish professors in the Czech university prior to 1938.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, that, that, was the end of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That is where I started, in '30-something '33, 1933, on the medical faculty of the German university, to study medicine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And got nearly to the end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, 1938, the Germans conquered, in a way-- diplomatically, without any shooting or war action-- the Sudetes, which were the German part of Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were England and France that had guaranteed they would help to preserve our country and give up at the last moment.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Chamberlain, who was the minister of the exterior at that time, came there and, and sold us out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Jews had to leave that part or were immediately arrested and transported to concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In this German part.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1938.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in Novem-- no, October 1938.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was, anyway, in Prague, which was still the, the--",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
